Star-Welcome

1. option to remove automount and add pmount + menu options.






Option to restart Tint2
Add tint2conf

https://crunchbang.org/forums/viewtopic.php?id=7449




#!/bin/bash
(killall -e tint2) &
(killall -e perl /usr/share/volwheel/volwheel) &
(sleep 1s && tint2) & 
(sleep 2s && /usr/bin/volwheel) & 
(sleep 5s && exit )

MainMenu (Super-Key + Space) --> Settings --> tint2 --> Restart tint2
